        ("The crowded bus moved slowly.", "ভৰা বাছে ধীৰে চলিছিল।", "Bhora baxe dhire colixil."),
        ("The folded clothes are in the bag.", "ভাঁজি ৰখা কাপোৰ বেগত আছে।", "Bãzi rakʰa kapur begôt ase."),
        ("The shining brass lamp lit the room.", "জলোৱা পিতলৰ প্ৰদীপে ঘৰ কৰিছিল।", "Jolowa pitôlôr prôdipe ghor korixil."),
