        ("The distant hills look blue in the evening.", "সন্ধিয়া দূৰৰ পাহাৰ নীলা দেখা যায়।", "Xondhiya durôr pahar nila dêkha jaẏ."),
        ("The upper floor has a better view.", "ওপৰৰ ফ্লোৰটোৰ দৃশ্য ভাল।", "Oporôr phloroṭôr drixx bhal."),
